{"id":232956859,"title":"#圖 男生燙髮經驗分享","content":"每次都被設計師鼓吹燙髮\n但心裡多少都會怕怕的\n怕燙完變成納豆哥（欸\n\n2020 該做點勇敢的嘗試\n幸好店長設計師沒有讓我失望\n圖片傷眼抱歉 可以忽略臉\nhttp://i.imgur.com/vMUXOow.jpg\nhttp://i.imgur.com/w91yCle.jpg\n一開始我只拿了一張網路相片\n跟她簡略的溝通\n她也一下子就明瞭我的想法\nhttp://i.imgur.com/uY5X7I9.jpg\n只能說\n第一次的體驗真的很重要\n燙的好壞 決定下一次的選擇\n\n💲價格部分\n剪燙洗共$1500\n算還能接受的價格\n供各位帥哥美女參考\n地點在屏東\n\n⏳時間部分\n我7點到\n等了一個小時才開始用…\n因為過年前變髮的人太多\n弄到10點 員工都走光了剩店長\n\nFinally\n這次整體體驗除了時間之外都很棒\n設計師怕我肚子餓 還請吃小上海\n不過那個藥水流下碰到我的臉\n當下很刺痛 有擦乾\n回去發現側臉部分燙傷脫皮\n真的不適合常燙 感覺很傷皮膚","excerpt":"每次都被設計師鼓吹燙髮，但心裡多少都會怕怕的，怕燙完變成納豆哥（欸，2020 該做點勇敢的嘗試，幸好店長設計師沒有讓我失望，圖片傷眼抱歉 可以忽略臉，一開始我只拿了一張網路相片，跟她簡略的溝通，她也一","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"62268850-d2b4-4c21-a7a3-26e71702a276","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-25T15:10:34.221Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T17:06:58.964Z","commentCount":3,"likeCount":10,"tags":[],"topics":["燙髮","捲髮"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"美髮","forumAlias":"hairsalon","school":"Arthur","department":"arthur_turing","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":10}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/vMUXOow.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/w91yCle.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/uY5X7I9.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"bceb6ddf-0b93-49ce-8675-6a46b19b7890","url":"https://i.imgur.com/vMUXOowl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/vMUXOowl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/vMUXOowl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-28T17:06:58.964Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T17:06:58.964Z"},{"id":"bceb6ddf-0b93-49ce-8675-6a46b19b7890","url":"http://i.imgur.com/vMUXOow.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/vMUXOow","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/vMUXOowl.jpg","typ